<subSubSection pageId="4" pageNumber="39" type="included species">
<paragraph pageId="4" pageNumber="39">Included species.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="4" pageNumber="39">
The genus presently includes only the type species, 
<taxonomicName authority="Dewulf &amp; Engel, 2014" authorityName="Dewulf &amp; Engel" authorityYear="2014" class="Insecta" family="Andrenidae" genus="Andrenopteryx" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Andrenopteryx willardi" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="39" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="willardi">Andrenopteryx willardi</taxonomicName>
